00:14:30,960 --> 00:14:34,200
 There was legacy databases that kind of learned SQL.

321
00:14:34,200 --> 00:14:36,480
 And there's lots of other databases.

322
00:14:36,480 --> 00:14:40,200
 SQLite is what we're actually gonna use with this course

