00:14:40,200 --> 00:14:43,120
 and it's super cool, super fast.

324
00:14:43,120 --> 00:14:45,080
 And on your cell phone,

325
00:14:45,080 --> 00:14:48,040
 you probably have 40 copies of SQLite.

326
00:14:48,040 --> 00:14:50,800
 And in your car, you probably have 40 copies of SQLite

327
00:14:50,800 --> 00:14:52,760
 'cause it's a real tiny embedded database.

328
00:14:52,760 --> 00:14:55,880
 It's not really good for a production scale

